headline: Credo Technology Group Holding (CRDO) Settles Patent Dispute With Amphenol Ending Legal Battles
summary: Credo Technology Group Holding (CRDO) recently secured a significant 95% price increase over the last quarter, coinciding with its settlement agreement with Amphenol that ended patent disputes on electrical cable technology. This favorable legal development likely added a sense of stability and confidence among investors. headline: AI Chips Today - Revolutionizing AI Infrastructure: VAST and SK Telecom Partnership
summary: VAST Data has partnered with SK Telecom to enhance South Korea's AI infrastructure using NVIDIA Blackwell supercomputers. This collaboration aims to create a virtualized GPU-as-a-Service environment, significantly reducing the time required to set up AI workloads from weeks to minutes, without compromising performance. By integrating VAST's AI Operating System with SK Telecom's Petasus AI Cloud, the infrastructure supports rapid AI model development and deployment entirely within South...
